137
00:07:59,593 --> 00:08:01,693
You idiot, why would you?

138
00:08:01,693 --> 00:08:03,393
That's true.

139
00:08:03,393 --> 00:08:04,463
Hurry it up, will you?

140
00:08:04,463 --> 00:08:05,993
Yeah.

141
