155
00:08:47,693 --> 00:08:50,293
I'm concerned about the voices I hear.

156
00:08:50,293 --> 00:08:52,511
I'm telling you to not worry about it.

157
00:08:52,693 --> 00:08:54,513
But...

158
00:08:54,513 --> 00:08:56,515
Don't get chicken!

159
00:08:56,515 --> 00:08:58,993
He could never let out a sound.

160
00:09:01,393 --> 00:09:04,523
Can't make a sound?

161
00:09:06,293 --> 00:09:08,793
Come on, hurry it up, will you?

162
00:09:08,793 --> 00:09:10,529
Yeah.

163
00:09:15,793 --> 00:09:17,693
The two just now...

164
00:09:17,693 --> 00:09:19,393
Don't tell me that they...

165
00:09:22,293 --> 00:09:25,593
Please wear my jacket for the time being.

166
00:09:25,593 --> 00:09:27,593
Thank you, you're a life-saver.

167
00:09:27,593 --> 00:09:28,547
You're welcome.

168
00:09:28,547 --> 00:09:31,693
We'd better hurry on out of here,

169
00:09:31,693 --> 00:09:33,993
