00:11:49,493 --> 00:11:52,393
If under normal circumstances, maybe,

228
00:11:52,393 --> 00:11:53,993
but with this stiff body,

229
00:11:53,993 --> 00:11:55,993
I don't think it's possible

230
00:11:55,993 --> 00:11:57,793
